                    and ending with stories of Musk's companies that were created on fleeting whims and
                    preposterously have the chance of completely changing the world (and galaxy). 
                    <br>
                    I would highly recommend reading this book to everyone I know. Musk's life demonstrates what 
                    its possible to build starting from near nothing and proves that our dreams 
                    and science fiction can become reality. More than that, the trials and tribulations 
                    undergone by Musk in building Tesla and SpaceX shed deep insight into how people behave,
